text: Stixis itzingeri is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1936.BioLib.cz - Stixis itzingeri. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1936 Category:Taxa named by Stephan von Breuning
